item.title: KittyORM Demo at Play Market
item.description:
Hi, check out KittyORM Demo at Google Play. KittyORM Demo application is not only some demo that would help you understand capabilities of KittyORM but also it is an interactive tutorial with build-in documentation, code snippets etc that would help to implement any KittyORM feature in your projects.
